## Next Actions
1. Trixie: dual-pass testing (delta + regression) on local build
2. Deploy to GitHub Pages or ship for user testing
3. Wrap as iOS app via WKWebView (Phase 2)

## Architecture Notes
- Pure HTML5 Canvas — no frameworks, no dependencies
- All rendering is procedural (no sprite sheets)
- Delta-time based physics for consistent speed across frame rates
- pointerdown event unified for touch + mouse
- Target: Chrome desktop + iPhone Safari
